ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this course to fellow students who want to practice critical thinking skills.
Summary: read (a lot of) articles, and discuss them. You will become a security-aware person. Definitely would recommend

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course has deepened my understanding in information security and raised my awareness of privacy. Through the discussion during the lectures, I practiced my critical thinking skills and gained more knowledge in information security and privacy.
